      "content": "it's not just about needing a rest though. it feels deeper than that. like, no matter how much i \"self-care,\" the reality doesn't change. the world is still hostile and i'm still stuck in this body/life that feels wrong. it's like there's no point in recharging if the battery is just gonna die again the same way tomorrow. i just feel so useless and heavy.",
